	flatpak build-bundle repo hello.flatpak org.flatpak.Hello --runtime-repo=https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
	flatpak install --user hello.flatpak 
	To uninstall, run flatpak remove org.flatpak.Hello 
